8x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slash">Slash</a>继女 Lucy-Bleu Knight 的死因已被公布。</p><p>上个月宣布<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slash-announces-death-of-stepdaughter-lucy-bleu-knight-aged-25-3776758">奈特于7月19日去世，享年25岁</a>。最初，关于她去世的更多信息没有公开分享，奈特的家人要求“在哀悼和​​处理这一毁灭性损失时，将社交媒体的猜测保持在最低限度”。</p><p>现在，洛杉矶县法医部门发表了一份声明，公布了她的死因和方式。</p><p>根据昨天（8月29日）分享的报告，该部门“确定25岁的Lucy-Bleu Knight的死因是硫化氢中毒”。它继续说：“死亡方式就是自杀。”</p><p>硫化氢是一种无色、剧毒气体，低浓度时可通过其刺鼻的臭鸡蛋气味来识别。疾病预防中心网站解释称，“吸入高浓度硫化氢会导致极快的昏迷和死亡”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C975hFTRMrF/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558